<anchor xml:id="_pa__linux__alsa_8h_1accc41e7fd89dc0a6163d54a4f25fb242"/><section>
    <title>PaAlsa_EnableRealtimeScheduling()</title>
<indexterm><primary>PaAlsa_EnableRealtimeScheduling</primary><secondary>pa_linux_alsa.h</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>pa_linux_alsa.h</primary><secondary>PaAlsa_EnableRealtimeScheduling</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>void PaAlsa_EnableRealtimeScheduling (<link linkend="_portaudio_8h_1a19874734f89958fccf86785490d53b4c">PaStream</link> * s, int enable)</computeroutput></para>
<para>Instruct whether to enable real-time priority when starting the audio thread.</para>

<para>If this is turned on by the stream is started, the audio callback thread will be created with the FIFO scheduling policy, which is suitable for realtime operation. </para>
</section>
